{"tid":2222253,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"技術員7.1涉掟水樽無擊中人 被控企圖襲警准保釋候訊","createTime":"2020-09-29T03:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T03:40:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"86be13020dcb0d13b80d0e75b6e76a606f1e69f8","tid":2222253,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"民陣發起今年7.1遊行但遭警方反對，大批市民仍到銅鑼灣一帶「行街」，有電腦技術員當天在時代廣場附近涉嫌向兩名警員丟水樽，惟未有擊中警員。事隔近三個月，技術員被控一項企圖襲警罪，案件今在東區法院提堂，裁判官應辯方申請，將案件押後再訊，被告獲准繼續保釋等候答辯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200929/4NHM375T5BF2RCI4NGTPAASLE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200929%2F4NHM375T5BF2RCI4NGTPAASLE4%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=81aecab8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200929%2F4NHM375T5BF2RCI4NGTPAASLE4%2F&h=a395c07a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200929/4NHM375T5BF2RCI4NGTPAASLE4/</a>"}]}